data.title: Official map of Dallas County, Texas
data.meta_description: Shows landownership. "Dallas, Texas, November 1st, 1886. I, J.M. Strong, County Surveyor of Dallas County, Texas, do hereby certify that the above and foregoing map is the latest and most correct representation of Dallas County, as compiled by me from the official records of said Dallas County, Texas." LC Land ownership maps, 945 Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image. Includes inset map of surrounding counties.
data.text:
The maps in the Map Collections materials were either published prior to 1922, produced by the United States government, or both (see catalogue records that accompany each map for information regarding date of publication and source).
